Welcome to Swing Pay

HELPING YOU TO REACH YOUR HR GOALS.....

Why " SWING PAY " ?

An elegant way to steer HR issues. With Swing Pay you can get rid of tedious spreadsheets/Excels. It makes all repetitive HRMS functions simpler, faster, and more efficient. Ensures that your employees have a world-class experience. Allows prioritizing work by getting operational HR out of the way.

Services

HR Management Software

It provides a means of storing employee data, managing payroll, time and attendance, and employee performance management.

Pay Stubs

Say no to mundane Spreedsheets!! An Automated breaking of CTC into basic, HRA, and other allowances will allows you to create the Pay Stubs in less time.

Leave Management System

With the help of swing pay your employees can apply for leaves and the management can approve or deny them on the go.

Timesheets

Timesheet helps you to track time on your projects while identifying billable and non-billable resources in your services business. It aids in measuring the utilization rate of your professional staff to allocate resources effectively.

Invoices

Using our automated billing and invoicing, reduces your time and cost. SwingPay also offers to mail your invoices to client and vendors with just a click away.

Reimbursements

SwingPay enables you and your employees to report expenses on the go, simplify approvals, and reimburse on time.

Service Requests

Service Requests system offered by the SwingPay enables your employees to raise requests category wise thereby they can view its status and can chat with the respective assignee.

Revenue Reports

No more manual calculations!! With SwingPay revenue reports you can get your monthly or yearly invoices and expenses in just a click away.

Monotonous with HR operations?
Here is the way to free yourself with Swing Pay
